  "title": "Stock Administrator (Luxury Retail - Stock / Inventory / Back of House) - Changi Airport",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is an international renowned Luxury goods brand and offers exciting job prospects. If you enjoy working in a vibrant luxury store surrounded with the latest Fashion items, this is what you are looking for!</strong></p><p></p><p></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Ensures the safety of the products and the valuable material in the store</li><li>Ensures that the goods in are entered into the IT system.</li><li>Lays out the products in the store according to the set criteria and place in designated shelving.</li><li>Prepares the products destined to the sales floor (anti-theft tag, price tag)</li><li>Prepares the goods for repairs/ returned send to repair lab, etc.</li><li>Perform Internal Outlet Transfer (IOT) whenever there’s request by the sales floor team.</li><li>Dispatches the goods to clients/factories/other stores or warehouses.</li><li>Prepare packing, scanning and process in system external transfer of goods to other countries in the Group.</li><li>Packing of past season goods to be delivered to Origin whenever items on the shop floor are not sold</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Candidates with warehouse / logistics experience are an advantage.</li><li>Can communicate well in English / Mother Tongue and blend well with the team.</li><li><strong>Willing to do retail shifts (5 day work week including weekends)</strong></li><li>Proficiency in Microsoft Office (Excel) is an advantage.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Retail sales candidates who wishes to switch to Inventory / Backend side are also welcomed.</strong></p><p><strong>Pay package will commensurate with experience.</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Interested candidates please submit your updated resume with recent photograph to <strong>gareth@quantumcareer.com</strong></p>",
